<p>58% of all Google searches happen on a smartphone. Google uses your mobile site. Not your desktop site. As the version it indexes and ranks. If your mobile experience is slow, broken, or incomplete, your rankings suffer across every device.</p>
<p>This guide covers everything you need to know about mobile SEO in 2026. We publish 3,500+ blog posts across 70+ industries and optimize every single one for mobile-first indexing before it goes live.</p>
