<h3>What This Means for Your Site</h3>
<p>Check <a href="/blog/google-search-console-guide/">Google Search Console</a> to see which Googlebot version crawls your pages. Under Settings, look for the "Crawler" section. It should show "Smartphone."</p>
<p>If your mobile site hides content behind tabs, loads key sections only after user interaction, or uses different URLs without proper canonicalization, you are losing indexable content.</p>
