<p>53% of mobile users abandon a site that takes longer than 3 seconds to load. The average mobile page takes 8.6 seconds. That gap costs rankings and revenue.</p>
<h3>Core Web Vitals on Mobile</h3>
<p><a href="/blog/improve-core-web-vitals/">Core Web Vitals</a> are Google's metrics for measuring real-world user experience. Only 40% of websites pass all 3 thresholds on mobile.</p>
